<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend\Controller\Router*  use urldecode() to decode URL params and return UTF-8 data. 
Zend\Controller\Action\Helper\Url.php -&gt;assemble() use urlencode() to encode params from UTF-8</p>

<p>Need replace urldecode() at html_entity_decode() and urlencode() at htmlentities(), because some servers use alternate encoding... not UTF-8.</p>

<p>Perhaps other modules also use urldecode (), urlencode ()
Zend\Http\Client.php
Zend\Http\Cookie.php</p>

